# Trivy ignore list for safe-mcp container images.
#
# Only add entries here with a written justification: a link to the upstream
# advisory, why the finding does not apply to our runtime, and (if possible)
# an expiry date by which we expect a fix. Unjustified entries are subject to
# removal during review.
#
# Format: one CVE-ID per line. Optional inline comment after a `#`.
#
# Example:
#   CVE-2024-00000  # not reachable - the vulnerable function is dead code in our build; expires 2026-06-30
